An action plan for election monitoring 25 July 2018 - 13 : 20 reading 37 times a national comment The Standing Committee of the Independent High Commission for Electoral Observation adopted a &quot; future action plan &quot; , especially in the area of information-management and civil society . The Independent Commission &apos;s statement , on Wednesday , reported that this action plan came after a series of meetings convened by the Commission under President Abdul Wahab Dahlal of of the Commission , throughout the days of completion and during which their work was assessed during the final stages .